1
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,766
Narrator: TEN, THE ABILITY
TO ENVELOP YOUR BODY

2
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:14,300
IN A SHROUD OF NEN AURA,

3
00:00:14,333 --> 00:00:18,000
MAKING IT TOUGHER AND
SLOWING THE EFFECTS OF AGING.

4
00:00:18,966 --> 00:00:20,233
ZETSU, A TECHNIQUE

5
00:00:20,266 --> 00:00:22,966
WHICH SHUTS OFF
YOUR FLOW OF NEN AURA,

6
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,933
EFFECTIVE FOR CONCEALING
YOUR PRESENCE

7
00:00:24,966 --> 00:00:26,900
AND RECOVERING FROM FATIGUE.

8
00:00:26,933 --> 00:00:32,166
REN, A TECHNIQUE FOR CREATING
AN ESPECIALLY STRONG NEN AURA.

9
00:00:32,233 --> 00:00:35,433
IT IS CRUCIAL
FOR INCREASING YOUR POWER.

10
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:39,466
HATSU, THE RELEASE
OF YOUR NEN AURA

11
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:41,833
AFTER USING REN TO BOOST IT.

12
00:00:41,900 --> 00:00:46,300
THESE FOUR ELEMENTS ARE KNOWN
AS THE FOUR EXERCISES

13
00:00:46,333 --> 00:00:50,500
AND ARE CRITICAL
TO THE MASTERY OF NEN.

14
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:52,466
♪

15
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:58,966
( singing in Japanese )

16
00:02:16,501 --> 00:02:19,267
Killua: GON, YOU AND ME,

17
00:02:19,334 --> 00:02:22,501
WE'VE GOTTA LEARN
ALL THAT WE CAN ABOUT NEN.

18
00:02:22,501 --> 00:02:24,501
( Gon chuckles )

19
00:02:24,534 --> 00:02:26,267
YEAH!

20
00:02:26,334 --> 00:02:28,234
♪

21
00:02:32,534 --> 00:02:34,034
Narrator: AFTER TWO MONTHS,

22
00:02:34,067 --> 00:02:36,567
DURING WHICH GON WAS FORBIDDEN
TO PRACTICE NEN,

23
00:02:36,601 --> 00:02:40,501
WING SUMMONED GON AND KILLUA
TO HIS ROOM FOR A MEETING.

24
00:02:42,501 --> 00:02:44,267
Wing: GON, KILLUA,

25
00:02:44,334 --> 00:02:48,667
STARTING TODAY, YOU WILL BE
TRAINING ALONGSIDE ZUSHI.

26
00:02:48,701 --> 00:02:50,267
AND, GON, SPLENDID WORK.

27
00:02:50,334 --> 00:02:53,267
I'M HAPPY TO SEE
THAT YOU KEPT YOUR PROMISE.

28
00:02:53,334 --> 00:02:55,234
IT'S BECAUSE
OF YOUR PROMISE THREAD.

29
00:02:55,267 --> 00:02:56,934
THERE WERE A COUPLE OF TIMES

30
00:02:57,001 --> 00:02:59,067
THAT I GOT REALLY CLOSE
TO GIVING IN,

31
00:02:59,101 --> 00:03:01,341
BUT THEN I'D LOOK AT THE THREAD,

32
00:03:01,374 --> 00:03:03,874
AND I COULD FEEL MYSELF
GETTING CALMER.

33
00:03:03,907 --> 00:03:06,841
Wing: BECAUSE I IMBUED IT
WITH NEN TO HELP YOU.

34
00:03:06,841 --> 00:03:08,007
Gon: WAIT. REALLY?

35
00:03:08,007 --> 00:03:10,407
Wing: NO. I WAS KIDDING.

36
00:03:10,441 --> 00:03:11,774
( Gon groans )

37
00:03:11,841 --> 00:03:13,174
Killua: HOLD ON.

38
00:03:13,207 --> 00:03:15,507
HOW CAN YOU TELL
GON'S BEEN KEEPING HIS PROMISE?

39
00:03:15,541 --> 00:03:16,507
AS FAR AS YOU KNOW,

40
00:03:16,541 --> 00:03:18,741
HE WAS SECRETLY CHEATING
THIS WHOLE TIME.

41
00:03:18,774 --> 00:03:20,174
( Gon groans )

42
00:03:20,207 --> 00:03:23,574
Wing: BECAUSE THE PROMISE THREAD
IS COMPLETELY INTACT.

43
00:03:23,607 --> 00:03:28,341
GON, I KNOW IT'S BEEN A WHILE,
BUT WOULD YOU SHOW ME YOUR TEN?

44
00:03:28,374 --> 00:03:29,341
Gon: YOU SURE?

45
00:03:29,374 --> 00:03:30,341
Wing: YES.

46
00:03:31,407 --> 00:03:32,174
Killua: OH, MAN.

47
00:03:32,207 --> 00:03:33,774
DO I EVEN REMEMBER HOW?

48
00:03:33,841 --> 00:03:36,007
Gon: IT'S BEEN SO LONG.

49
00:03:36,041 --> 00:03:39,174
I WONDER IF I
CAN STILL PULL IT OFF.

50
00:03:49,207 --> 00:03:51,541
Wing: WHAT DO YOU THINK, ZUSHI?

51
00:03:51,574 --> 00:03:53,574
Zushi: IT‐‐IT'S AMAZING.

52
00:03:53,607 --> 00:03:56,574
HIS AURA IS FLOWING
COMPLETELY AROUND HIM, SIR!

53
00:03:56,607 --> 00:04:02,581
IT'S SOFT AND TRANQUIL,
BUT IT'S‐‐IT'S SO POWERFUL, TOO!

54
00:04:02,614 --> 00:04:05,214
Gon: THAT'S IT! WHAT A RELIEF.

55
00:04:05,247 --> 00:04:08,181
MAN, I WAS WORRIED
I HAD FORGOTTEN HOW TO DO IT!

56
00:04:08,214 --> 00:04:10,014
Wing: ONCE YOU'VE
LEARNED THE TECHNIQUE,

57
00:04:10,014 --> 00:04:11,247
IT CAN'T BE FORGOTTEN.

58
00:04:11,281 --> 00:04:13,914
HOWEVER, IN ORDER
TO BECOME A TRUE MASTER,

59
00:04:13,947 --> 00:04:16,381
YOU WILL HAVE
TO PRACTICE DILIGENTLY.

60
00:04:16,414 --> 00:04:19,681
Gon: BUT IT FELT A LOT EASIER
THAN IT DID BEFORE,

61
00:04:19,681 --> 00:04:22,881
AND I HAVEN'T PRACTICED TEN
IN A REAL LONG TIME.

62
00:04:22,914 --> 00:04:24,547
Wing: I CAN EXPLAIN.

63
00:04:24,581 --> 00:04:27,681
THAT'S BECAUSE YOU'VE BEEN
TRAINING YOUR SPIRIT EVERY DAY.

64
00:04:27,681 --> 00:04:29,881
NOW PLEASE LOOK
AT YOUR LEFT HAND.

65
00:04:29,914 --> 00:04:31,281
Gon: HUH?

66
00:04:31,347 --> 00:04:32,281
( gasps )

67
00:04:32,347 --> 00:04:34,514
IT BROKE!

68
00:04:34,514 --> 00:04:38,114
Wing: I TIED THE THREAD
TO YOUR FINGER WITH MY OWN NEN,

69
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:40,214
SO IF YOU
HAD BROKEN YOUR PROMISE,

70
00:04:40,247 --> 00:04:42,681
THE THREAD
WOULD HAVE BROKEN AS WELL.

71
00:04:42,714 --> 00:04:45,014
Killua: YOU CAN
DO STUFF LIKE THAT?

72
00:04:45,047 --> 00:04:46,881
QUESTION, MR. WING‐‐

73
00:04:46,914 --> 00:04:49,081
YOU SAW HISOKA
AND KASTRO'S MATCH?

74
00:04:49,114 --> 00:04:50,447
Wing: YES, I DID.

75
00:04:50,514 --> 00:04:52,281
Killua: SO WHAT
WAS HISOKA'S ABILITY?

76
00:04:52,347 --> 00:04:54,514
DO YOU THINK WE COULD DO THAT,

77
00:04:54,547 --> 00:04:57,014
SEND OUR LIMBS FLYING
ALL OVER THE PLACE?

78
00:04:57,047 --> 00:04:59,414
Wing: HMM.
THAT'S A DIFFICULT QUESTION.

79
00:04:59,447 --> 00:05:02,687
GON, HAVE YOU SEEN
A RECORDING OF THE FIGHT?

80
00:05:02,721 --> 00:05:05,887
Gon: NO. NOT YET, SIR. EH?

81
00:05:05,921 --> 00:05:09,421
Wing: THEN I'LL EXPLAIN
WHILE WE WATCH.

82
00:05:12,354 --> 00:05:13,521
( crowd cheering )

83
00:05:17,187 --> 00:05:19,854
Wing: THERE.
SEE THE STRANDS OF AURA

84
00:05:19,854 --> 00:05:21,854
EXTENDING OUT
FROM HIS LEFT HAND?

85
00:05:21,887 --> 00:05:23,587
Gon: STRANDS OF AURA?

86
00:05:23,621 --> 00:05:27,021
Wing: YES. DO YOU SEE THEM?

87
00:05:27,021 --> 00:05:28,287
( boys groan )

88
00:05:28,354 --> 00:05:30,187
Gon: NO, I DON'T THINK SO.

89
00:05:30,187 --> 00:05:31,954
Killua: I CAN'T SEE ANYTHING.

90
00:05:32,021 --> 00:05:33,587
Zushi: ME NEITHER, SIR.

91
00:05:33,621 --> 00:05:36,087
( Gon grunts )

92
00:05:36,121 --> 00:05:40,521
ARE THERE REALLY STRANDS OF AURA
COMING OUT OF HIS LEFT HAND?

93
00:05:40,554 --> 00:05:41,587
ARE YOU SURE?

94
00:05:41,621 --> 00:05:44,721
Wing: I AM. SEE,
HISOKA IS USING A TECHNIQUE

95
00:05:44,754 --> 00:05:48,021
THAT MAKES HIS AURA EXCEEDINGLY
DIFFICULT TO PERCEIVE.

96
00:05:48,021 --> 00:05:52,354
IT'S A HIGH‐LEVEL APPLICATION
OF ZETSU, KNOWN AS "IN."

97
00:05:52,354 --> 00:05:57,021
IT RENDERS EVEN POWERFUL AURA
INVISIBLE TO YOUR OPPONENT.

98
00:05:57,021 --> 00:05:58,354
AND TO COUNTER THIS,

99
00:05:58,354 --> 00:06:02,061
YOU MUST FOCUS ALL YOUR REN
IN BOTH OF YOUR EYES

100
00:06:02,094 --> 00:06:04,694
UTILIZING A TECHNIQUE
KNOWN AS GYO.

101
00:06:04,727 --> 00:06:10,894
THE METHOD GON USED IN HIS FIGHT
WITH GIDO MIGHT ALSO BE USEFUL,

102
00:06:10,927 --> 00:06:13,227
BUT YOU CAN'T COUNTERATTACK,

103
00:06:13,261 --> 00:06:15,527
SO YOU'D ULTIMATELY
GET YOURSELF KILLED.

104
00:06:17,027 --> 00:06:18,127
Gon: RIGHT.

105
00:06:18,194 --> 00:06:20,694
Wing: MY ASSIGNMENT
FOR THE TWO OF YOU

106
00:06:20,694 --> 00:06:24,427
IS TO PRACTICE REN UNTIL YOU
CAN SEE THROUGH HISOKA'S IN.

107
00:06:24,461 --> 00:06:26,894
Zushi: BUT, MASTER,
WHAT ABOUT ME?

108
00:06:26,927 --> 00:06:29,194
WHAT KIND OF TRAINING
SHOULD I DO?

109
00:06:29,194 --> 00:06:33,194
Wing: ZUSHI, YOU SHOULD
ALREADY BE JUST STRONG ENOUGH

110
00:06:33,194 --> 00:06:35,361
TO SEE PAST HISOKA'S IN.

111
00:06:35,394 --> 00:06:36,927
Zushi: YOU THINK SO?

112
00:06:36,961 --> 00:06:39,927
Wing: IF YOU WOULD,
PLEASE SHOW THEM YOUR REN.

113
00:06:39,961 --> 00:06:41,361
Zushi: UH...

114
00:06:41,361 --> 00:06:43,194
( grunts )

115
00:06:43,194 --> 00:06:45,561
O‐OSU!

116
00:06:45,594 --> 00:06:47,527
( chorus vocalizing )

117
00:06:49,761 --> 00:06:51,261
( inhales )

118
00:06:52,594 --> 00:06:53,761
( grunts )

119
00:06:53,794 --> 00:06:54,861
REN!

120
00:06:54,894 --> 00:06:56,194
( Gon and Killua gasp )

121
00:06:56,194 --> 00:06:58,761
Gon: IT'S SO STRONG.

122
00:06:58,794 --> 00:07:00,867
IT'S JUST AS BIG AS OURS,

123
00:07:00,901 --> 00:07:03,967
BUT THE AURA
IS SO MUCH MORE DENSE.

124
00:07:04,034 --> 00:07:06,767
Wing: NOW FOCUS THAT AURA
INTO YOUR EYES.

125
00:07:06,801 --> 00:07:08,101
Zushi: OSU!

126
00:07:10,034 --> 00:07:12,901
( grunting )

127
00:07:16,867 --> 00:07:18,767
AND GYO!

128
00:07:18,801 --> 00:07:20,567
Wing: GOOD. SO TELL ME,

129
00:07:20,601 --> 00:07:23,767
CAN YOU SEE THE AURA
RUSHING FROM HIS BODY?

130
00:07:23,801 --> 00:07:25,901
Zushi: EH...

131
00:07:28,401 --> 00:07:30,367
YES.

132
00:07:30,401 --> 00:07:32,734
Wing: THERE ARE
INDIVIDUAL STRANDS OF AURA.

133
00:07:32,767 --> 00:07:34,967
HOW MANY OF THEM DO YOU SEE?

134
00:07:35,034 --> 00:07:36,567
Zushi: 12.

135
00:07:36,601 --> 00:07:37,634
WAIT. NO.

136
00:07:37,701 --> 00:07:39,567
I THINK I COUNT 13, SIR.

137
00:07:39,601 --> 00:07:43,567
Wing: NOT QUITE,
BUT YOU ARE VERY CLOSE INDEED.

138
00:07:43,601 --> 00:07:44,701
( Zushi groans )

139
00:07:44,734 --> 00:07:46,034
( panting )

140
00:07:46,034 --> 00:07:47,967
I REALLY COULD SEE THEM.

141
00:07:48,034 --> 00:07:50,534
Wing: YOU'RE REALLY MAKING
EXCELLENT PROGRESS, ZUSHI.

142
00:07:50,567 --> 00:07:53,467
Zushi: OSU! THANK YOU!
I'M TRYING, MASTER.

143
00:07:53,534 --> 00:07:56,567
Wing: BY CHANNELING EVERY OUNCE
OF YOUR POWER THROUGH GYO,

144
00:07:56,601 --> 00:08:00,067
YOU ACHIEVED A LEVEL WHERE YOU
COULD SEE THROUGH HISOKA'S IN.

145
00:08:00,101 --> 00:08:01,707
BUT WITH ENOUGH TRAINING,

146
00:08:01,741 --> 00:08:05,374
YOU'LL BE ABLE TO USE GYO
EVEN WHILE YOU'RE FIGHTING.

147
00:08:05,407 --> 00:08:06,641
♪

148
00:08:06,707 --> 00:08:08,574
NOW DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

149
00:08:08,607 --> 00:08:10,241
FIRST, PRACTICE USING REN,

150
00:08:10,274 --> 00:08:12,874
AND MASTER THE APPLICATION
KNOWN AS GYO.

151
00:08:12,874 --> 00:08:15,107
THEN, AND ONLY THEN,

152
00:08:15,141 --> 00:08:18,641
WILL YOU DISCOVER THE TRUE
NATURE OF HISOKA'S ABILITY.

153
00:08:18,707 --> 00:08:22,874
YOU ASKED IF YOU WOULD EVER BE
ABLE TO USE THAT SAME ABILITY,

154
00:08:22,874 --> 00:08:24,541
AND MY ANSWER IS YES,

155
00:08:24,574 --> 00:08:26,374
BUT AT THE SAME TIME, NO.

156
00:08:26,374 --> 00:08:27,307
( both gasp )

157
00:08:27,374 --> 00:08:29,374
Wing: REGARDLESS
OF WHAT HIS POWER IS,

158
00:08:29,374 --> 00:08:33,374
SO LONG AS IT USES NEN,
YOU'LL BE ABLE TO LEARN IT,

159
00:08:33,374 --> 00:08:35,074
BUT IT'S IMPORTANT TO NOTE

160
00:08:35,107 --> 00:08:37,374
THAT NEN ABILITIES
DEPEND ON THE INDIVIDUAL,

161
00:08:37,374 --> 00:08:39,541
BECAUSE OF COURSE
WE EACH POSSESS

162
00:08:39,541 --> 00:08:42,074
DIFFERENT SPECIALTIES
AND PREFERENCES,

163
00:08:42,107 --> 00:08:44,874
WHICH MEANS THAT NEN
DIFFERS FOR EACH PERSON.

164
00:08:44,874 --> 00:08:48,041
IF YOU'RE SERIOUS
ABOUT MASTERING NEN,

165
00:08:48,074 --> 00:08:50,741
YOU SHOULDN'T MERELY COPY
THE ABILITIES OF OTHERS.

166
00:08:50,774 --> 00:08:53,941
YOU NEED TO FIRST IDENTIFY
YOUR OWN PARTICULAR STRENGTHS.

167
00:08:53,974 --> 00:08:56,707
Killua: STRENGTHS, HUH?

168
00:08:56,707 --> 00:08:58,274
Wing: YOU'RE STILL GROWING,

169
00:08:58,307 --> 00:09:01,381
SO YOU HAVEN'T SETTLED
ON ONE FORM YET.

170
00:09:01,381 --> 00:09:05,047
MY ADVICE IS TO ENRICH YOURSELF
AS MUCH AS POSSIBLE.

171
00:09:05,081 --> 00:09:07,647
THAT IS THE PURPOSE
OF YOUR TRAINING.

172
00:09:07,714 --> 00:09:09,714
TRAIN WITH ALL OF YOUR MIGHT.

173
00:09:09,747 --> 00:09:12,914
PLAY JUST AS HARD,
AND ENJOY LIFE.

174
00:09:12,947 --> 00:09:15,047
Boys: OSU!

175
00:09:15,081 --> 00:09:17,114
Wing: I BELIEVE THE LAST DAY

176
00:09:17,147 --> 00:09:19,881
OF KILLUA'S WINDOW TO COMPETE
IS JUNE NINTH.

177
00:09:19,881 --> 00:09:22,447
AND, GON,
YOURS IS THE TENTH, CORRECT?

178
00:09:22,481 --> 00:09:26,881
BOTH OF YOU SHOULD REGISTER
TO FIGHT ON YOUR FINAL DAY.

179
00:09:26,881 --> 00:09:29,381
IN THE MEANTIME, YOU'LL TRAIN.

180
00:09:29,381 --> 00:09:32,547
YOU MUST BOTH LEARN GYO
BEFORE YOU ENTER BATTLE.

181
00:09:32,581 --> 00:09:34,481
Boys: OSU!

182
00:09:35,881 --> 00:09:38,581
Gon: HEY, ZUSHI,
YOUR REN WAS IMPRESSIVE.

183
00:09:38,614 --> 00:09:42,381
YOU GOT WAY AHEAD OF US
WHILE I WAS STUCK RECUPERATING.

184
00:09:42,381 --> 00:09:45,481
Zushi: NO. I'VE STILL
GOT A LONG WAY TO GO.

185
00:09:45,547 --> 00:09:48,047
Gon: HEY, WHY DON'T
WE PRACTICE A LITTLE?

186
00:09:48,047 --> 00:09:49,447
IT SHOULD BE FUN.

187
00:09:49,481 --> 00:09:52,814
Killua: OKAY. THEN LET'S
GO UP TO YOUR ROOM, GON.

188
00:09:52,881 --> 00:09:53,981
Gon: MM‐HMM.

189
00:10:00,387 --> 00:10:01,821
( gasps )

190
00:10:01,854 --> 00:10:04,387
ZUSHI, KILLUA...

191
00:10:04,421 --> 00:10:05,387
Zushi: I FEEL IT.

192
00:10:05,421 --> 00:10:07,821
Killua: WE'VE GOT COMPANY, GUYS.

193
00:10:07,821 --> 00:10:10,421
( elevator bell dings )

194
00:10:12,321 --> 00:10:14,254
♪

195
00:10:18,721 --> 00:10:20,921
YOU DON'T GIVE UP, DO YOU?

196
00:10:20,987 --> 00:10:23,321
THAT ISN'T THE WAY
TO MAKE FRIENDS.

197
00:10:23,321 --> 00:10:25,554
Man: NOW THAT'LL BE
ENOUGH OF THAT.

198
00:10:25,587 --> 00:10:28,254
JUST TELL US WHEN
YOU'RE GOING TO FIGHT,

199
00:10:28,321 --> 00:10:31,321
BECAUSE I'M DYING
TO BE YOUR OPPONENT. HEH.

200
00:10:31,321 --> 00:10:32,487
( Killua scoffs )

201
00:10:32,521 --> 00:10:35,487
I GUESS THESE GUYS
SPECIALIZE IN HUNTING NEWBIES.

202
00:10:35,487 --> 00:10:39,354
THIS IS WHAT THEY DO,
GET WINS BEATING US UP.

203
00:10:39,387 --> 00:10:41,987
Man: WE'RE GETTING
DESPERATE HERE.

204
00:10:41,987 --> 00:10:44,254
SEE, OUR DEADLINE
IS APPROACHING.

205
00:10:44,321 --> 00:10:46,687
COME ON. WE WANNA FIGHT. HEH.

206
00:10:46,721 --> 00:10:51,654
I'LL EVEN DEMONSTRATE MY POWER
FOR YOU RIGHT HERE AND NOW.

207
00:10:51,654 --> 00:10:54,321
HOW ABOUT THAT? HEH.

208
00:10:55,321 --> 00:10:56,587
‐ ( Zushi gasps )
‐ Gon: OKAY.

209
00:10:56,654 --> 00:10:59,587
I'M GOING TO BE FIGHTING
ON JUNE THE TENTH.

210
00:10:59,654 --> 00:11:00,894
Killua: HEY! GON!

211
00:11:00,927 --> 00:11:03,361
Man: THAT WON'T WORK FOR ME.

212
00:11:03,394 --> 00:11:07,494
I'M SORRY TO TELL YOU,
BUT MY DEADLINE IS MAY 29th.

213
00:11:07,527 --> 00:11:09,061
FIGHT ON THAT DAY.

214
00:11:09,094 --> 00:11:12,094
Killua: WHO CARES ABOUT
YOUR STUPID DEADLINE, YOU IDIOT?

215
00:11:12,161 --> 00:11:13,527
LET'S GET GOING.

216
00:11:14,727 --> 00:11:17,494
Man: GON, MY FRIEND...

217
00:11:17,527 --> 00:11:19,761
YOU AND I WILL FIGHT.

218
00:11:19,827 --> 00:11:22,227
I GUARANTEE IT. HEH.

219
00:11:23,161 --> 00:11:25,694
IT'S A PROMISE.

220
00:11:25,727 --> 00:11:28,327
Killua: COME ON. IGNORE HIM.

221
00:11:29,227 --> 00:11:31,161
Riehlvelt:
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

222
00:11:31,194 --> 00:11:34,827
Man: I'M GOING
TO FORCE HIM TO FIGHT ME.

223
00:11:34,827 --> 00:11:36,927
HEH HEH.

224
00:11:44,397 --> 00:11:47,430
Killua: VISUALIZE ENERGY
BUILDING UP IN YOUR BODY.

225
00:11:47,464 --> 00:11:51,997
FEEL THE POWER FROM EACH
AND EVERY CELL GATHERING,

226
00:11:52,064 --> 00:11:54,330
GROWING AND GROWING.

227
00:11:54,397 --> 00:11:57,564
THEN, ALL OF A SUDDEN,
FORCE THAT POWER OUT!

228
00:12:02,437 --> 00:12:03,570
( boys sigh )

229
00:12:03,604 --> 00:12:05,804
Gon: I'M GETTING THE HANG OF IT.

230
00:12:05,837 --> 00:12:09,004
Killua: THE TIMING TO GET TEN
TO CONTAIN THAT AURA

231
00:12:09,070 --> 00:12:10,570
WAS A LITTLE BIT TRICKY.

232
00:12:10,570 --> 00:12:11,804
Zushi: WAIT. A LITTLE?!

233
00:12:11,837 --> 00:12:15,237
HOW ARE THEY
PICKING IT UP SO FAST?

234
00:12:15,237 --> 00:12:17,570
Gon: BUT ZUSHI'S AURA
IS STRONGER.

235
00:12:17,570 --> 00:12:20,270
WE'RE NOT EVEN CLOSE
TO MATCHING HIM YET.

236
00:12:20,304 --> 00:12:22,270
Killua: GUESS WE
OUGHT TO TRAIN MORE.

237
00:12:22,304 --> 00:12:23,837
Zushi: UH, N‐NO! THAT'S ENOUGH.

238
00:12:23,904 --> 00:12:27,237
LEARNING WHEN TO REST
IS A BIG PART OF TRAINING.

239
00:12:27,237 --> 00:12:29,304
WHY DON'T WE
JUST CALL IT A DAY?

240
00:12:29,337 --> 00:12:30,904
Killua: REALLY? 'CAUSE I CA‐‐

241
00:12:30,937 --> 00:12:32,604
Zushi: I TOLD YOU NO!

242
00:12:32,637 --> 00:12:35,470
IF THEY SURPASS ME
IN HALF A DAY,

243
00:12:35,504 --> 00:12:37,304
I'LL LOSE ALL MY MOTIVATION.

244
00:12:37,337 --> 00:12:38,837
Killua: WHAT'S THE DEAL?

245
00:12:38,904 --> 00:12:42,004
Gon: OH, IT'S FINE.
SO MORE TOMORROW?

246
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:43,437
Killua: WORKS FOR ME.

247
00:12:44,737 --> 00:12:47,004
Zushi: I'LL SEE YOU
AGAIN TOMORROW.

248
00:12:47,070 --> 00:12:48,437
Gon: TAKE IT EASY.

249
00:12:53,904 --> 00:12:55,504
Killua: ALL RIGHT, THEN.

250
00:12:55,570 --> 00:12:57,504
( overlapping chatter )

251
00:12:57,570 --> 00:12:59,237
( elevator bell dings )

252
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:06,744
Man: HEH.

253
00:13:16,944 --> 00:13:18,444
( sighs )

254
00:13:19,977 --> 00:13:21,444
( Zushi gasping )

255
00:13:27,577 --> 00:13:31,744
I CAN'T‐‐I CAN'T MOVE!

256
00:13:31,744 --> 00:13:35,910
I CAN'T TALK OR BREATHE EITHER.

257
00:13:35,944 --> 00:13:37,410
WHAT'S GOING ON?

258
00:13:41,744 --> 00:13:43,244
Riehlvelt: OOPS.

259
00:13:49,244 --> 00:13:50,944
Man: IT'S YOUR TURN.

260
00:13:50,977 --> 00:13:53,277
Gido: ALL RIGHT.

261
00:13:57,177 --> 00:13:58,644
Man: HEH HEH.

262
00:13:58,677 --> 00:14:00,784
‐ Killua: KNOCK IT OFF.
‐ ( man gasps )

263
00:14:02,650 --> 00:14:06,017
Killua: I FIGURED
YOU MIGHT BE UP TO SOMETHING.

264
00:14:06,084 --> 00:14:09,817
BUT FORGET THE DIRTY TRICKS.
YOU WANT A FIGHT, FINE.

265
00:14:09,850 --> 00:14:12,617
WHICH DAY DO YOU WANT?

266
00:14:12,650 --> 00:14:16,317
OH, AND DON'T WORRY.
I'LL LET YOU WIN, OKAY?

267
00:14:16,350 --> 00:14:19,917
WAIT. HOW ABOUT
I GIVE ALL OF YOU A WIN?

268
00:14:19,950 --> 00:14:22,250
GOOD ENOUGH?

269
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:26,784
Man: ONCE I GET
MY WIN AGAINST YOU,

270
00:14:26,817 --> 00:14:29,517
YOUR FRIEND GON
WILL BE MY NEXT VICTIM.

271
00:14:29,584 --> 00:14:31,517
Killua: IF YOU WANNA FIGHT GON,

272
00:14:31,584 --> 00:14:33,917
YOU'LL HAVE TO WORK
AROUND HIS SCHEDULE.

273
00:14:33,917 --> 00:14:36,750
SOMETHING TELLS ME
HE'LL BE HAPPY TO.

274
00:14:37,984 --> 00:14:40,484
IN FACT, I CAN GUARANTEE IT.

275
00:14:40,517 --> 00:14:42,517
Man: HEH HEH HEH HEH.

276
00:14:42,584 --> 00:14:43,517
OKAY.

277
00:14:43,584 --> 00:14:45,950
IF THE TWO OF YOU
ARE WILLING TO FIGHT,

278
00:14:45,984 --> 00:14:49,117
IT'LL SAVE US THE TROUBLE
OF USING TACTICS LIKE THIS ONE.

279
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:52,117
Riehlvelt: WHAT DO YOU SAY
WE ALL REGISTER TOGETHER?

280
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:56,317
ONCE THAT'S DONE,
WE'LL RETURN THE BOY UNHARMED.

281
00:14:56,350 --> 00:14:58,650
Killua: YEAH, SURE. OKAY.

282
00:14:58,684 --> 00:15:01,424
BUT THIS IS ABSOLUTELY
THE VERY LAST TIME.

283
00:15:01,424 --> 00:15:02,424
YOU GOT THAT?

284
00:15:02,457 --> 00:15:05,024
( pen scratching )

285
00:15:05,090 --> 00:15:07,857
THERE. MAY 29th.

286
00:15:07,924 --> 00:15:10,590
DONE. YOU HAPPY NOW?

287
00:15:10,590 --> 00:15:13,957
Man: YES.
WE'LL RETURN YOUR FRIEND HERE.

288
00:15:15,457 --> 00:15:18,357
Killua: AND UP WE GO.

289
00:15:19,990 --> 00:15:22,924
OH. I'LL SAY IT AGAIN.

290
00:15:22,924 --> 00:15:24,190
IT'S THE LAST TIME.

291
00:15:24,257 --> 00:15:26,357
AND IF YOU BREAK YOUR PROMISE‐‐

292
00:15:26,424 --> 00:15:29,924
( groans ) WHATEVER.

293
00:15:29,924 --> 00:15:31,024
FORGET IT.

294
00:15:31,090 --> 00:15:32,590
Riehlvelt: WHAT? I'M CURIOUS.

295
00:15:32,590 --> 00:15:35,590
Man: WHAT'S GOING TO HAPPEN
IF WE BREAK OUR PROMISE?

296
00:15:35,590 --> 00:15:38,257
Killua: THERE'S NO POINT
IN TELLING YOU NOW.

297
00:15:38,290 --> 00:15:40,924
JUST KEEP YOUR END
OF THE DEAL, OKAY?

298
00:15:41,990 --> 00:15:43,657
Man: HEH HEH.

299
00:15:43,690 --> 00:15:44,790
( rings )

300
00:15:47,457 --> 00:15:50,590
Gido: HELLO? IS THIS GON?

301
00:15:50,590 --> 00:15:52,524
♪

302
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:57,990
I DON'T THINK I HAVE
TO TELL YOU WHAT THIS MEANS.

303
00:15:59,157 --> 00:16:01,264
AS LONG AS YOU DON'T TELL ANYONE

304
00:16:01,297 --> 00:16:03,697
AND YOU FOLLOW MY INSTRUCTIONS
TO THE LETTER,

305
00:16:03,764 --> 00:16:06,997
THE THREE OF YOU
WILL BE ABLE TO TRAIN TOMORROW

306
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:09,097
JUST LIKE YOU PLANNED.

307
00:16:09,130 --> 00:16:11,297
( Gon gasps )

308
00:16:11,330 --> 00:16:12,797
ZUSHI.

309
00:16:15,430 --> 00:16:17,030
( peg leg thumping )

310
00:16:19,130 --> 00:16:21,930
Man: SO HOW DID IT GO WITH GON?

311
00:16:21,930 --> 00:16:24,664
Gido: PERFECTLY.
HE'S REGISTERED FOR THE 30th.

312
00:16:24,697 --> 00:16:27,764
Man: HEH HEH.
THAT MAKES TWO VICTORIES.

313
00:16:27,764 --> 00:16:29,097
TOO EASY.

314
00:16:29,130 --> 00:16:30,597
HEH HEH HEH.

315
00:16:35,797 --> 00:16:39,497
Killua: NOT KILLING PEOPLE IS
HARDER THAN I THOUGHT IT'D BE.

316
00:16:39,530 --> 00:16:43,430
AH, MAN.
HONEST LIVING IS TOUGH.

317
00:16:45,030 --> 00:16:46,930
( overlapping chatter )

318
00:16:50,830 --> 00:16:54,430
Scalper: STEP RIGHT UP!
GET YOUR TICKETS HERE!

319
00:16:54,430 --> 00:16:57,197
THESE ARE HOT OFF THE PRESSES,
LADIES AND GENTS!

320
00:16:57,264 --> 00:16:58,997
GON VERSUS SADASO!

321
00:16:59,030 --> 00:17:00,370
( Killua gasps )

322
00:17:00,437 --> 00:17:02,604
Scalper: WE'VE GOT KILLUA
VERSUS SADASO, TOO!

323
00:17:02,637 --> 00:17:06,270
BETTER BUY 'EM NOW,
OR YOU'RE GONNA REGRET IT!

324
00:17:06,304 --> 00:17:07,270
Killua: HEY, POPS.

325
00:17:07,304 --> 00:17:08,504
Scalper: 'SUP, KID?

326
00:17:08,537 --> 00:17:11,437
Killua: THAT SADASO GUY
HAS JUST ONE ARM?

327
00:17:11,437 --> 00:17:12,704
Scalper: THAT'S RIGHT.

328
00:17:12,770 --> 00:17:15,704
THE ONE‐ARMED FIGHTER
WITH A FACE LIKE A MASK.

329
00:17:15,770 --> 00:17:18,770
IF HE GRABS YOU
WITH HIS INVISIBLE LEFT ARM,

330
00:17:18,770 --> 00:17:19,770
YOU'RE DONE.

331
00:17:19,804 --> 00:17:22,704
SEE, THEY CALL HIM
THE NEWBIE HUNTER, AND‐‐

332
00:17:22,770 --> 00:17:24,504
♪

333
00:17:24,537 --> 00:17:26,504
Killua: THAT SON OF A...

334
00:17:28,137 --> 00:17:29,470
( door closes )

335
00:17:29,989 --> 00:17:31,422
Gon: KILLUA? HEY.

336
00:17:31,422 --> 00:17:34,655
Killua: GON.
THIS IS WHERE YOU'VE BEEN?

337
00:17:34,689 --> 00:17:36,289
Gon: UH, YEAH.

338
00:17:36,322 --> 00:17:40,289
Wing: KILLUA, I HEAR THAT YOU
HELPED ZUSHI HOME LAST NIGHT.

339
00:17:40,322 --> 00:17:41,189
THANK YOU.

340
00:17:41,255 --> 00:17:43,155
Killua: ARE YOU
FEELING ALL RIGHT?

341
00:17:43,189 --> 00:17:44,422
Zushi: YEAH. I'M FINE.

342
00:17:44,422 --> 00:17:46,789
I WAS PROBABLY JUST TIRED.
THAT'S ALL.

343
00:17:46,822 --> 00:17:48,822
I'M SORRY TO WORRY YOU.

344
00:17:48,855 --> 00:17:50,355
Killua: OH. HEY, MR. WING,

345
00:17:50,422 --> 00:17:53,422
DO YOU THINK THAT WE
CAN WATCH THAT VIDEO AGAIN?

346
00:17:53,422 --> 00:17:57,422
'CAUSE I FIGURED OUT
HOW TO USE GYO.

347
00:17:57,422 --> 00:17:58,689
‐ Wing: EH?
‐ Gon: AHH!

348
00:17:58,755 --> 00:18:01,429
Zushi: HUH? REALLY?

349
00:18:01,429 --> 00:18:03,362
♪

350
00:18:10,429 --> 00:18:12,362
( somber chorus singing )

351
00:18:14,429 --> 00:18:17,129
Killua: 15 THREADS, RIGHT?

352
00:18:17,162 --> 00:18:20,262
13 FOR THE CARDS,
ONE MORE FOR THE SCARF,

353
00:18:20,295 --> 00:18:23,629
AND ONE WELL‐HIDDEN ONE
FOR THE ARM HE TOSSED.

354
00:18:23,662 --> 00:18:25,329
AND THEN...

355
00:18:25,362 --> 00:18:26,529
KEEP GOING.

356
00:18:28,162 --> 00:18:31,595
HISOKA'S AURA,
IT ALMOST LOOKS LIKE...

357
00:18:31,629 --> 00:18:33,995
IT'S EXPANDING AND CONTRACTING.

358
00:18:34,029 --> 00:18:39,095
OR DOES IT ATTRACT CERTAIN
OBJECTS LIKE A MAGNET DOES?

359
00:18:39,095 --> 00:18:41,095
HOW ELSE WOULD HIS ARM
REATTACH ITSELF?

360
00:18:41,095 --> 00:18:45,929
NOT TO MENTION FLYING OFF
AND TARGETING KASTRO'S JAW?

361
00:18:46,795 --> 00:18:47,929
MY MONEY IS ON THE FORMER.

362
00:18:47,962 --> 00:18:51,095
I THINK HIS AURA
MUST BE STRETCHY,

363
00:18:51,095 --> 00:18:52,695
LIKE RUBBER OR SOMETHING.

364
00:18:52,762 --> 00:18:54,262
AND IF IT IS,

365
00:18:54,262 --> 00:18:57,495
THEN THAT WOULD EXPLAIN
MOST OF HIS MAGIC TRICKS.

366
00:18:57,529 --> 00:18:58,962
( Killua exhales )

367
00:18:58,995 --> 00:19:00,195
( Zushi gasps )

368
00:19:00,262 --> 00:19:02,935
HE'S ON A COMPLETELY
DIFFERENT LEVEL.

369
00:19:02,935 --> 00:19:05,602
Wing: YOU PASS.
THAT'S VERY GOOD.

370
00:19:05,602 --> 00:19:08,169
ALTHOUGH, I AM
A LITTLE SURPRISED.

371
00:19:08,202 --> 00:19:10,669
I CERTAINLY NEVER
EXPECTED BOTH OF YOU

372
00:19:10,702 --> 00:19:12,702
TO ACTUALLY LEARN GYO OVERNIGHT.

373
00:19:12,769 --> 00:19:15,435
‐ ( Killua gasps ) BOTH OF US?
‐ Gon: YEP,

374
00:19:15,469 --> 00:19:18,802
BUT I STILL COULDN'T FIGURE OUT
WHAT HISOKA'S ABILITY WAS.

375
00:19:18,835 --> 00:19:21,102
‐ ( Zushi sighs )
‐ Wing: SO, KILLUA,

376
00:19:21,135 --> 00:19:23,935
I'M SURE NOW THAT YOU'VE
FINISHED YOUR ASSIGNMENT,

377
00:19:23,935 --> 00:19:26,269
YOU'LL BE WANTING
TO FIGHT SOON, CORRECT?

378
00:19:26,302 --> 00:19:30,102
Gon: IT'S OKAY. I DIDN'T MEAN
TO BEAT YOU TO THE PUNCH.

379
00:19:30,135 --> 00:19:33,102
I GUESS I JUST GOT AN ITCH
TO FIGHT. THAT'S ALL.

380
00:19:33,135 --> 00:19:36,202
Killua: YEAH. I UNDERSTAND.

381
00:19:36,269 --> 00:19:39,435
THEY MUST HAVE
THREATENED YOU, HUH, GON?

382
00:19:39,435 --> 00:19:43,502
ACTUALLY, I'VE ALREADY
CHOSEN MY DAY TO FIGHT.

383
00:19:43,535 --> 00:19:45,535
I SIGNED UP FOR MAY 29th.

384
00:19:45,602 --> 00:19:47,369
Gon: I'M FIGHTING ON MAY 30th.

385
00:19:47,435 --> 00:19:49,202
Wing: ALL RIGHT, FINE.

386
00:19:49,269 --> 00:19:51,669
I GUESS I UNDERESTIMATED
YOUR PROGRESS.

387
00:19:51,702 --> 00:19:53,269
IT'S QUITE IMPRESSIVE.

388
00:19:53,269 --> 00:19:55,602
BETWEEN NOW
AND YOUR SCHEDULED FIGHTS,

389
00:19:55,602 --> 00:19:57,935
PRACTICE BOTH TEN AND REN,

390
00:19:57,935 --> 00:20:00,169
AND IN ADDITION
TO YOUR TRAINING,

391
00:20:00,202 --> 00:20:02,742
GET PLENTY OF REST AND SLEEP.

392
00:20:02,775 --> 00:20:04,275
Killua and Gon: OSU!

393
00:20:04,309 --> 00:20:05,809
♪

394
00:20:05,875 --> 00:20:07,242
‐ Gon: KILLUA...
‐ Killua: HMM?

395
00:20:07,275 --> 00:20:10,742
Gon: THOSE GUYS THREATENED YOU,
TOO, DIDN'T THEY?

396
00:20:10,775 --> 00:20:13,042
THAT MAKES ME SO MAD.

397
00:20:13,075 --> 00:20:15,375
Killua: YEAH. BUT STILL,

398
00:20:15,409 --> 00:20:18,642
MY BIGGEST CONCERN
WAS GETTING WING'S PERMISSION.

399
00:20:18,709 --> 00:20:20,875
Gon: I GUESS MY BIGGEST CONCERN

400
00:20:20,909 --> 00:20:24,442
IS THAT THEY'LL DO
THE SAME THING TO ZUSHI AGAIN.

401
00:20:24,475 --> 00:20:26,075
Killua: IT'S OKAY.

402
00:20:27,109 --> 00:20:29,375
YOU DON'T NEED TO WORRY.

403
00:20:30,575 --> 00:20:32,942
♪

404
00:20:32,975 --> 00:20:36,875
Sadaso: TODAY, I'LL BEAT
KILLUA FOR MY SIXTH WIN.

405
00:20:36,909 --> 00:20:39,542
TOMORROW, I'LL BEAT GON
FOR MY SEVENTH WIN.

406
00:20:39,575 --> 00:20:44,742
AFTER THAT, ALL I'LL NEED TO DO
IS FIND THREE MORE SUCKERS.

407
00:20:44,775 --> 00:20:46,109
HEH HEH HEH.

408
00:20:46,142 --> 00:20:48,042
THEN I'LL BE A FLOOR MASTER.

409
00:20:48,042 --> 00:20:51,109
WITH THE KIND OF FAME
AND FORTUNE THAT'LL GET ME,

410
00:20:51,142 --> 00:20:53,742
I'LL BE SET
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

411
00:20:53,775 --> 00:20:55,409
( gasps )

412
00:20:57,709 --> 00:20:59,875
Killua: YOU MOVE, YOU DIE.

413
00:20:59,909 --> 00:21:02,449
YOU USE NEN, AND YOU DIE.

414
00:21:02,482 --> 00:21:04,915
MAKE A SOUND, AND YOU DIE.

415
00:21:04,949 --> 00:21:08,049
IF YOU UNDERSTAND,
CLOSE YOUR EYES.

416
00:21:09,315 --> 00:21:10,549
DO YOU SEE WHAT HAPPENS

417
00:21:10,582 --> 00:21:12,815
WHEN YOU BREAK YOUR PROMISES?

418
00:21:13,915 --> 00:21:16,149
IF YOU DO, OPEN YOUR EYES,

419
00:21:16,215 --> 00:21:19,882
LOOK AT ME IN THE MIRROR,
AND LISTEN CAREFULLY.

420
00:21:22,582 --> 00:21:27,782
DON'T EVER SHOW YOUR DIRTY FACE
IN FRONT OF US AGAIN.

421
00:21:27,815 --> 00:21:29,482
YOU'LL KEEP THIS PROMISE.

422
00:21:29,549 --> 00:21:32,149
♪

423
00:21:34,715 --> 00:21:36,382
Referee: SADASO'S TIME IS UP!

424
00:21:36,415 --> 00:21:38,115
KILLUA WINS BY DEFAULT!

425
00:21:38,149 --> 00:21:39,882
‐ ( crowd groaning )
‐ Man: ARE YOU KIDDING ME?!

426
00:21:39,915 --> 00:21:42,549
‐ Man #2: WHAT IS THIS?!
‐ Man #3: BOO!

427
00:21:42,582 --> 00:21:44,482
Narrator:
KILLUA OPENS THE BATTLE

428
00:21:44,549 --> 00:21:47,915
AGAINST THE PERSISTENT TRIO
WITH A TECHNICAL VICTORY.

429
00:21:47,949 --> 00:21:50,815
THANKS TO THEIR
UNIQUE NATURAL TALENTS,

430
00:21:50,882 --> 00:21:52,815
THE REAL BATTLE AT HEAVENS ARENA

431
00:21:52,882 --> 00:21:55,915
IS ONLY JUST BEGINNING
FOR GON AND KILLUA,

432
00:21:55,949 --> 00:21:59,382
WHO ARE LEARNING NEN
AT INCREDIBLE SPEED.

433
00:22:01,955 --> 00:22:04,089
( singing in Japanese )

434
00:23:11,895 --> 00:23:13,762
Gon: COMING UP, GON...

435
00:23:13,795 --> 00:23:14,795
Killua: AND KILLUA'S...

436
00:23:14,829 --> 00:23:16,129
Both: HUNTERPEDIA!

437
00:23:19,538 --> 00:23:20,271
Gon: I'M GON.

438
00:23:20,304 --> 00:23:21,371
Killua: I'M KILLUA.

439
00:23:21,404 --> 00:23:22,938
Both: AND THIS IS
OUR HUNTERPEDIA!

440
00:23:22,971 --> 00:23:24,371
Gon: TODAY
WE'LL BE INTRODUCING SADASO!

441
00:23:24,404 --> 00:23:26,571
HE WENT THROUGH
THE TRADITIONAL INITIATION

442
00:23:26,604 --> 00:23:28,404
WITH GIDO AND RIEHLVELT.

443
00:23:28,438 --> 00:23:31,604
Killua: ONE ARM'S INVISIBLE,
'CAUSE IT'S MADE OF NEN.

444
00:23:31,638 --> 00:23:32,704
Gon: THAT'S RIGHT!

445
00:23:34,271 --> 00:23:36,204
♪

446
00:23:37,371 --> 00:23:39,871
Gon: NEXT TIME,
"POWER TO AVENGE."

447
00:23:39,871 --> 00:23:41,071
POWER?

448
00:23:42,038 --> 00:23:43,438
Killua: AVENGE?

